5. Give two reasons as to why a NoSQL database system would be preferred to an SQL one.
----------------------------
Two reasons to prefer NoSQL:
1.Scalability: No SQL databases scale horizontally and are well suited to large, distributed systems.
2.Flexible Schema: No SQL supports dynamic, unstructured data. Ideal for agile development and evolving requirements.




